{"title":"Aventon’s New Soltera.2 eBike Promises High-Tech and Low-Cost","link":"https://bikerumor.com/aventon-soltera-2-ebike-class-ii-or-class-iii/","date":1691499697000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 featured Image\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-featured-Image-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>California-based <a href=\"https://www.aventon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">eBike specialists</a>, Aventon are launching a new eBike called the Soltera.2. This new eBike brings a load of updates over the OG Soltera. The Soltera.2 ships as a Class 2 eBike, with both pedal assist and throttle. The throttle is removable in case the place you want to ride prohibits throttle usage. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 step-through in motion\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-step-through-in-motion-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Photo c. Aventon </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Like the original Soltera, the new Soltera.2 comes in either a step-over frame or a step-through frame, and 4 sizes, regular and large, in both frame styles. Four different levels of pedal assist are available to the Soltera.2 rider, Eco, Tour, Sport, and Turbo. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While the Soltera.2 ships as a Class II ebike, you can unlock the ability to run it as a Class III which will hit pedal-assisted speeds of 25mph. This feature is accessible through the Aventon App. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"305\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344-800x305.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 display\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344-800x305.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344-297x113.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344-120x46.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344-768x293.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-display-e1691422854344.jpeg 1276w\" /></a><figcaption>Big, bright display</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>With the torque sensor, your pedaling effort is detected and then seamlessly amplified, giving you “just the right amount of assist when you need it most on long rides or commutes across town”. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 sitting with bikes\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-sitting-with-bikes.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Sitting, Soltera.2 in Midnight Black (L), and Storm Blue (R).</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Rocking the same lightweight aluminum frame as its predecessor makes riding the Soltera.2 enjoyable on flat terrain, while allowing you to conquer the hills or carry it up a flight or two of stairs. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"345\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535-800x345.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 headlight\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535-800x345.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535-297x128.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535-120x52.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535-768x331.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-headlight-e1691422496535.jpeg 1276w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Integrated head and tail lights, along with built-in turn signals add to the rider’s safety and confidence when sharing the road with both motorists and pedestrians. A single charge is said to give the Soltera.2 riders up to 46 miles of range (using PAS Eco throughout flat terrain, with a rider weight of 160 lbs).</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 Storm Blue step through\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Storm-Blue-step-through.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Step-Through frame in Storm Blue</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 Ghost White Step trough\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Ghost-White-Step-trough.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Step-Through frame in Ghost White</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 Citrine yellow traditional\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-Citrine-yellow-traditional.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Traditional frame in Citrine Yellow</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Key Soltera.2 Updates</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"341\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk-800x341.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 traditional frame crosswalk\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk-800x341.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk-297x126.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk-120x51.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk-768x327.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-traditional-frame-crosswalk.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"341\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life-800x341.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 train life\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life-800x341.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life-297x126.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life-120x51.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life-768x327.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-train-life.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Battery: </strong>Features a removable internal Lithium-ion 36V 9.6Ah, (360Wh) battery with LG cells, certiﬁed to the TUV Rheinland standard in compliance with UL 2849</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Stem:</strong> Features smoother welds on the collar folding area, accompanied by a slightly more relaxed steering angle that improves handling.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Handlebar:</strong> Features a 31.8mm/680mm aluminum riser bar.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Drivetrain:</strong> Features a new 3-piece 170mm crank-set that pairs well with the new torque sensor technology, crank-arms, spider, and 48t chainring</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Throttle: </strong>On-demand 20mph without pedaling located on the left side of the handlebar</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Headlight: </strong>Now features an integrated powered 300 Lumens headlight. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Rear Lights:</strong> Now features integrated turn signals and braking ﬂash.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Graphic: </strong>Now features a bold new frame graphic.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Soltera.2 Retail, Sizing, and Specifications</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held.jpeg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"800\" height=\"534\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held-800x534.jpeg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 dive side held\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held-800x534.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-dive-side-held.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>Traditional frame in Midnight Black</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retail: </strong>$1399 (free shipping directly to your home) or order it through Aventon’s 1000+ <a href=\"https://www.aventon.com/pages/electric-bike-shop-dealer-locator\" target=\"_blank\">dealer network</a></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>4 sizes:</strong> (based on height)</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Regular Standard Frame: 5’3″ – 5’10”</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Large Standard Frame: 5’10” – 6’4″</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Regular Step-Through: 4’11” – 5’7″</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Large Step-Through: 5’7″ – 6’1″</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Specifications:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-specsheet.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"613\" height=\"729\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-specsheet.jpg\" alt=\"Aventon Soltera.2 specsheet\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-specsheet.jpg 613w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-specsheet-252x300.jpg 252w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/Aventon-Soltera.2-specsheet-101x120.jpg 101w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.aventon.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Aventon.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/aventon-soltera-2-ebike-class-ii-or-class-iii/\">Aventon’s New Soltera.2 eBike Promises High-Tech and Low-Cost</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"44587364d226244a3539b1d56b96f99ba1c7c90802ba6aa1eaacae3376c88731","category":"Cycling"}